reviewText: Boobalicious is here. I saw this online and knew I needed it. I absolutely fell in love with this funny and yet very great animated series. Simply a boy seems to have lost his memory and once two beautiful women appear before him and this girl he living with things get a little out of control and he begins to remember. After having an encounter with the two women he finds the other girl and seems she has a special talent like the other two a pair of... Well as the title says Boobalicious. She and young boy get together surprising the other two women with her gifts and his reactions to her. All in with the series being great and the animation is better than I had remembered. Great product with no objections from me. Definitely recommended for anyone in a spot for some Boobalicious fun. Product arrived quickly with no complaints and no damage.
